{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_04_03",
  "title": "サニーピース 04 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "星村さんから話を聞いて、私は星見プロの\n新人オーディションを受けることになったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After hearing from Hoshimura-san‚ I decided to\naudition for Hoshimi Prods's new talent",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "その日、偶然再会したから\n縁がつながって星見プロに巡り会ったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That day‚ we met again by chance‚\nand through fate‚ I came across Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "凄いね！　本当に運命って感じだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing! It really feels like fate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9560318311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、星見プロのオーディションを受けて\n初めて三枝さんと会ったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I auditioned for Hoshimi Prods‚\nand met Saegusa-san for the first time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 744.8029836000032,
          "startTime": 23.1448029836
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんだなんだ、俺の名前が聞こえたと思ったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow-wow‚ I thought I heard my name‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1534696262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "随分と懐かしい話をしているじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you're talking about something so nostalgic",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん！　おはようございます！　今、遙子ちゃんが\n星見プロを受けた時の話を聞いてたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san! Good morning! I was listening to\nHaruko-chan talk about when she auditioned for Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遙子のオーディションか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko's audition…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.407163938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの時のことはよく覚えているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember that time very well",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "面接での遙子さんはどんな感じだったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What was Haruko-san like at the interview?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0926287335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだな……遙子の第一印象は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… my first impression of Haruko was",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.908978065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「この子はアイドルに向いていない」だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'She's0 not cut out to be an idol'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、三枝さんにもそう思われていたんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it‚ Saegusa-san thought the same way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.12058781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ああ、誤解しないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ don't get me wrong",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8507919154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "才能がないという意味じゃないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mean you're not talented",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ただ……この子は、この業界でやっていくには",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just… this girl‚ too kind to survive",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5155086519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "優し過ぎると思ったのさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in this industry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.1659848851
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.1659848851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なるほど……キミはそんなに沢山のオーディションを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… so you've taken so many auditions",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2159848851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "受けて、ことごとく落選してきたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and failed them all",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4347603799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "（うう……どうしてオーディションに落ちた話なんて）\n（しちゃったのかしら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh… why did I tell him that I failed）\n（the audition…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "（これじゃ、自分でアイドルに向いてないって）\n（言ってるようなものだわ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That's practically saying I'm not cut out to）\n（be an idol…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2141707421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルへの意欲はある、人柄も申し分ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have the desire to be an idol‚ and you have the personality",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2141707421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "真面目で努力家なのも好印象だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's also good impression that you're honest and hard-working",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だが、それだけでやっていけるほどこの業界は甘くない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ this industry isn't so easy to get by with this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1525588672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それは分かるね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You understand that‚ don't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.1140310287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "言うまでもないことだが、今はアイドル同士が対決して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Needless to say‚ these days‚ idols compete with each other",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1140310287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ランキング上位を奪い合う時代だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to take the top seats in the rankings",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "優しいキミに、他のアイドルを蹴落としてでも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're kind‚ so do you have the courage to rise to the top‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2572963714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "上に上がろうという気概はあるのかい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "even if it means kicking other idols out of the way?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.0312726657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "……誰かを蹴落とすとか、足を引っ張るとか\nそういうのは正直言って苦手です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……To be honest‚ I'm not good at\nkick someone or pushing people down",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.3548552195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "私はみんなで仲良く\n力を合わせてアイドル業界を盛り上げていきたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want everyone to get along‚\nand work together to liven up the idol industry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.010304737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんなで仲良くか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone getting along…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.010304737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "やはりキミはアイドルに向いていないようだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess you're not cut out to be an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.0999959309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "向いてないってよく言われます……でも\n向いてない人がアイドルを目指しちゃいけないんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm often told that I'm not cut out for it… but\nshouldn't people who aren't cut out for it not aim to become idols?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2999959309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.7596397716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "私はそうは思いません。大事なのは向いているかどうか\nじゃない、自分を信じて想いを貫けるかどうかです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think so. What's important isn't whether you're cut out for it\nor not‚ but whether you believe in yourself and stick to your guns!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.1333292643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
